As Chris explained to me when I wrote a Deep Dive on Hadrian [ https://subs=
tack.com/redirect/1cf3c1b5-d15b-4d61-b4fe-3d12f75f2ac9?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3Qi=
fQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] in April 2022, =E2=80=9CI =
ended up deciding that the only way to really fulfill the mission was to go=
