It seems to be working. Hadrian is worth [ https://substack.com/redirect/84=
3a7607-9cbd-4392-a442-70eca80fbdc1?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaM=
ZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] roughly $500 million expects to reach $30 mill=
ion in revenue this year as a three-year-old company.=20
When I started writing Part II, my plan was to leave the Hadrian example at=
