); text-decoration: underline;">A Dynamic Model of Process and Product Inno=
vation</a><span>. </span></em><span>By looking at a study of 120 firms, the=
y found that </span><strong>product innovation </strong><span>is initially =
dominant but gradually gives way to </span><strong>process innovation</stro=
