 new technologies is slow at the beginning and incumbents resist it.</stron=
g></em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px=
; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That is a long quote, but if you =
